# Atlassian Integration
# Required for Jira and Confluence MCP operations
ATLASSIAN_DOMAIN=yourcompany.atlassian.net
JIRA_USER_EMAIL=you@company.com
JIRA_API_TOKEN=your-api-token-here

# Setup Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env (do not commit .env to git)
# 2. Replace placeholder values with your actual credentials
# 3. For Jira API token: https://id.atlassian.com/manage-profile/security/api-tokens
